WEBVTT

00:04:28.960 --> 00:04:34.319
they realized that on the basis of love
and compassion, they are the same.

00:04:34.320 --> 00:04:36.360
So think, you are all thinkers.

00:04:38.109 --> 00:04:42.109
(Singing) Unthinking he reads the Gita
But it fails to brush his thoughts

00:04:49.767 --> 00:04:53.767
Kabir says, listen sadhus,
people are lost in coming and going.

00:04:57.146 --> 00:05:04.166
(Music)